rComments: He is a very good professor who adapts to his students learning styles and is the most engaging professor during masterclasses. He is very funny and musical with great ideas! I always learn a lot when he is teaching :)
It is all about the music and helping students develop as musicians when he teaches. Creates a welcoming and fun environment with inspirations and creativity.
An extremely gifted and caring pedagogue who is more than just a teacher. He is an inspiration and role model who elevates all his students. The best professor for piano at the University of Toronto.
